{"tid":1246382,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"野餐前廢廢地護膚分享","createTime":"2019-06-20T16:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T17:18:56.000Z","uid":187825,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1fce5aaad1765c9149947908f0c82b34c13e32ea","tid":1246382,"uid":187825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"大家而家即刻敷返個<strong>純保濕</strong>Mask先 為聽日皮膚做好準備<br />\n（千祈唔好用清潔、美白mask，磨砂都唔好）<br />\n其實都講完架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁趁住敷mask依個時間 就執定野餐袋先 咁聽日就可以瞓多五分鐘喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都唔知聽日實際會係咩天氣 最好帶定長遮啦 曬又用得落雨又用得 帶多把去借比朋友用都得<br />\n有啲咩係SPF400就係頭帽喇 記住帶埋Eyes Mask 同埋口罩 （而家天氣都差，懸浮粒子好多 用防毒果種都不為過 N95都未必夠）最好自己帶自己用啦 <br />\n唔係人地借左比你 佢就冇得用曬黑哂架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好 其實都講哂喇 早睡早起 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"448e0f0d8748ea57dd11d05a5ab2d88887778800","tid":1246382,"uid":187825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:58:07.000Z","msg":"仲要差爆尿袋 唔驚自拍冇電 <br />\n會合到自己要見既人 就關數據 享受大自然"},{"pid":"ee42838c15c05f6cecabdc27e801909404537b1c","tid":1246382,"uid":65390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"自己帶支水<br />\n飲多啲水皮膚先好<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想整花個妝<br />\n買支有jit jit樽口嘅水方便唔駛掂到自己情況下飲用"},{"pid":"e9efcd2acb6744e48870603c068d9f1f6c73a9d5","tid":1246382,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"仲有帶退熱貼<br />\n同寶礦力粉 (齋飲水唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n朱古力/能量棒<br />\n高熱量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋風扇仔/或者執份報紙撥吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061a596b4ab99ad53365c9e56e7e7a864f75f7d9","tid":1246382,"uid":42970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}